#

Pumpkin Spice Smoothie

5 min
$3.5
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

SmoothieBreakfastHealthyFall Flavors

Description

A creamy and delicious pumpkin smoothie that’s perfect for a quick breakfast or snack, packed with nutrients and fall flavors!

Ingredients

  • canned pumpkin puree: 1/2 cup
  • banana: 1 medium
  • vanilla yogurt: 1 cup
  • milk (or almond milk): 1/2 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1 tablespoon
  • ice cubes: 1 cup
